For this iteration, I'll focus on adding relative clauses to improve flow.

```diff
<<<<<<< SEARCH
    sentence += ", ".join(clauses) + "."
>>>>>>> REPLACE
    sentence += " and ".join(clauses) + "."
```
Please fix it to the correct format.
